data.description: Rare opportunity for primary home or investment in an amazing location near the beltline. Almost half an acre lot brimming with mature shrubs that bloom beautifully come springtime. No HOA. Plenty of storage in the walkout garage/ basement with safe room/ vault for your valuables. One-level living with gorgeous hardwood floors, large picture windows, & fireplace. Walk up Blue Ridge Road to the fairgrounds or take a short drive to Downtown Raleigh and Cary, NC Museum of Art + trails, Dix and Pullen Parks, NCSU, or RDU Airport.
